dkf.config

Interface ConfigurationInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Configuration

    public interface ConfigurationInterface
    The root interface in the Configuration hierarchy. A configuration is a set of parameters, which are used by the DKF framework to set up a Federate on the specific RTI infrastructure.
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    SMASH-Lab University of Calabria
